page.title: 08Clubs in Queensbury
page.content: Queensbury has not got a centre like some towns as it only a small village. There is not alot of things there. There is only:- 1 Youth Club 3 Disco's 24 Public House's and 1 Golf Club Queensbury is mostly all grassland and trees. Golf Club In the golf club we have around 70 members we get a lot of contributions towards the club as well as ordinary members we have social members. We have a shop at the side of the club. We do alot of catering for the people who come to the club. We have alot of competitions in the golf club.
